	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Waouh !<delay8 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> C'est vrai que si tu te mets
